Package com.deco2800.game.components.story

Interface StoryBase

All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicDialogue, CutScene
public interface StoryBase
A story base object is what the manager calls upon to control the story.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    boolean advance()
    Advance the story.
    void create()
    Creates the story
    void display()
    Displays the story.
    void dispose()
    Dispose the story
    boolean isDead()
    Returns if the story has already been disposed
